## Iterate

- **Apply feedback** — export JSON from the feedback panel, then run in Claude Code:
  ```
  /prototype apply-feedback feedback-<timestamp>.json
  ```
- **Explore a variant** — fork into an alternative direction:
  ```
  /prototype variant "more corporate"
  ```

## Deploy (optional)

Drop this folder on any static host — Vercel, Netlify, GitHub Pages, S3. No build required.

```
# Vercel
npx vercel --prod

# Netlify
npx netlify deploy --prod --dir=.
```

